                        <a href="tel:+74952230523" class="hover:text-indigo-600 dark:hover:text-indigo-400 transition-colors">+7 495 223-05-23, доб. 1709</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-indigo-500 shrink-0"><rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"/><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/></svg>
