                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 pt-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-center md:text-left">
                © {currentYear} Факультет информационных технологий Московского Политеха
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 flex items-center gap-1.5">
                Разработано с
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-red-500 mx-0.5"><path d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z"/></svg>
                <a href="https://t.me/edducon" target="_blank" class="font-bold text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 hover:underline">@edducon</a>
